<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    As she explains in the last chapter, she was worried that her thoughts about killing the mule would actually alert the mule to her suspicions and she <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    As she explains in the last chapter, she was worried that her thoughts about killing the mule would actually alert the mule to her suspicions and she chose the less risky action of killing Mis. She did not know that the mule was not reading her thoughts, so she probably could have gotten away with it after all<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
